---
description: Implementation plan for the social share preview module ŌĆö build-time Playwright render of one canonical 1200├Ś630 og.png plus App Router metadata wiring.
intent: >
  Build the social share preview module at src/service/socialShare ŌĆö move the
  in-repo HTML design source into the module, self-host JetBrains Mono so the
  render does not depend on Google Fonts, wire a Playwright prebuild script
  that screenshots the .og element to public/og.png at 1200├Ś630 under 300 KB,
  export an ogImage metadata config from the orchestrator, and extend the
  root layout's metadata so every statically-exported page emits the full
  Open Graph and Twitter Card tag set pointing at the one canonical image.
---

