        `metadata.title.default` / `metadata.description` ŌĆö those continue
        to drive per-page titles via Next's merge semantics. Per-page
        `metadata` exports that supply their own `openGraph.title` or
        `description` inherit everything else (including `images`), which
        satisfies the spec's "per-page overrides permitted as an additive
        nicety" contract without any additional work.
      - Everything else in `layout.tsx` ŌĆö GTM, `CanonicalTag`,
        `ExpoTipProvider`, `Expo`, font variable ŌĆö is unchanged.

